description: SlugLord is a fresh and unique creation from Matt Furie, designed as a slug version of his original character, Pepe the Frog. Artists frequently evolve their creations, and Furie introduced SlugLord as a twist on the iconic Pepe. The SLUGLORD token is a meme coin aimed at creating a strong community of fans of both SlugLord and Matt Furie.
